      "review_title": "Good game! There’s only one problem…",
      "review_description": "This game is really good, the only problem is that it gets really repetitive after some time since the ingredients are always the same. I would personally add missions that you can do to get more ingredients. I’m pretty sure that it could make the game much more bought.",
