      "id": "976095548911266",
      "score": 4,
      "review_title": "Cooking Clash",
      "review_description": "Really fun game, really exciting also! the only cons with this game are that the food that the customers want has a certain time limit for you to hurry up to finish the food. And if you don't finish the food on time, the customers will lash out at you and attack you by throwing rocks. Another con is that the customers can steal your money left on counter and then run away. Last con with this game is that a burglar can break in and kill customers and steal your money. Luckily, you can stop him by killing him. Last,last,last con of the game is that customers can attack you if you accidentally give them the wrong food.",
